title: [Vornavis, Wooded Plains]
description: Moths and fireflies flit about this area of woodland, moving from bush to bush in breathtaking displays of light and motion.  Many of the bushes here have no leaves, and many empty cocoons can be found hanging from tree branches and bush limbs.

Moths and butterflies flit about this area of woodland, moving from bush to bush in breathtaking displays of color and motion.  Many of the bushes here have no leaves, and many empty cocoons can be found hanging from tree branches and bush limbs.
